Gourmet Wine & Cheese Board Thank You Gift Set
List.Description:
This is a beautiful gift of savory edibles with an attractive cutting board and cheese knife. Creamy cheese, crackers, mustard, sausage, biscotti and more are paired with the juicy, ripe fruit flavors of Kenwood's Vintage Red Blend.

Wine Gift Includes:

  • Kenwood Vintage Red Blend:
    A delicious red wine with flavors of raspberry and plum, combined with toasty vanilla oak and spicy notes of white pepper. This wine is exceptionally well balanced, with approachable tannins and a smooth finish.

  • Beef Summer Sausage 5 oz
  • Sonoma Jacks Pepper Jack Cheese 4 oz
  • Sesame Crackers 2 oz
  • Napa Mustard 1.75 oz
  • California Crunchy Herb Almonds 1.5 oz
  • Chocolate Biscotti .9 oz
  • Cheese Spreader
  • Wood Cheese Board
  • Festive Greet Sheet

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment.

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.
